useTransition:-React ka hook hai jo heavy state updates ko low priority bana deta hai, taaki UI smooth rahe aur app hang na ho.Iska use tab karte hain jab large data filter, search ya rendering ho rahi ho. Jaise bade table me search karte waqt input slow ho sakta hai. useTransition me hum important update (typing) ko pehle aur heavy update ko baad me kar dete hain.




