Error Boundary:-Yeh Hamre App Ko Crush Hone Se Baachta hai Like Kisse Child Ke Andar Koi Error Aajata Hai To KKya hote hai ki Jo Hamre Application Hai Pure Crush Ho jaati Hai Agar Kisse Child Component Me Error Aaya Too

Agar kisi child component me error aa gaya: <User /> aur uske andar: undefined.name  to normally poori screen white ho jayegi. Error Boundary lagane par:  <ErrorBoundary>
  <User />
</ErrorBoundary>  agar User me error aaya, to poori app crash nahi hogi. Sirf fallback UI dikhega:

Kaha use karte hain:
Large components
API data wale components
Charts
Dashboard
Third-party libraries
Kisi risky component ke around


Short me:

try-catch JS ke liye
Error Boundary React component errors ke liye


Most:- React me mostly class component se banta hai. Function component me direct Error Boundary nahi banta, lekin use kar sakte ho.

Aajkal function component wale project me bhi use karte hain, bas ErrorBoundary khud class wala rehta hai ya library use karte hain.


npm install react-error-boundary



import { ErrorBoundary } from "react-error-boundary";

function ErrorFallback() {
  return <h1>Something went wrong</h1>;
}

function App() {
  return (
    <ErrorBoundary FallbackComponent={ErrorFallback}>
      <Profile />
    </ErrorBoundary>
  );
}



To aaj function component ke project me bhi Error Boundary use hota hai, bas class ke jagah library use kar lete hain
