BrowserRouter:-BrowserRouter React Router ka main wrapper component hota hai. Yeh browser ke current URL ko listen karta hai aur uske according correct component render karta hai. Jaise agar URL /dashboard hai to Dashboard component dikhayega. Hum poore app ko BrowserRouter me wrap karte hain kyunki Route, Link, useNavigate jaise saare routing features isi ke andar kaam karte hain. Agar BrowserRouter na ho to routing ka context nahi milega aur error aayega.
