useNavigate:-useNavigate ek hook hai jo code ke through page navigation ke liye use hota hai. Jab button click, login, submit ya kisi condition ke baad route change karna ho, tab useNavigate use karte hain.useNavigate React Router ka hook hai jo programmatically page change karne ke liye use hota hai.
const navigate = useNavigate();
