Virtual List aur Infinite Scroll 


Virtual List: Sare data memory me hota hai, par screen par sirf visible items render hote hain. Jaise 10,000 items hain par ek time par sirf 20 dikh rahe hain. Performance fast hoti hai.
Infinite Scroll: Jab user niche scroll karta hai tab naya data API se load hota rehta hai. Sare data pehle se nahi hota.



Example:

Virtual List = 10,000 users already aaye hue hain, par render sirf visible users hote hain.
Infinite Scroll = Pehle 20 users aaye, fir scroll par next 20, fir next 20.



React me:

Virtual List ke liye commonly react-window ya react-virtualized use hota hai.
Infinite Scroll ke liye manually scroll event ya react-infinite-scroll-component use karte hain.



